{ The following 2 model games examine sidelines features some sidelines that White can choose after } 1. e4 c6 2. Nf3 d5 3. Nc3 dxe4 4. Nxe4 Nf6 5. Qe2 Nxe4 6. Qxe4 Be6 { More specifically, we deal with the continuations 7.Be2 and 7.Qf4. Even though these moves are not challenging, Black should have good understanding of the arising structures. } *[Event "POL-ch"]
