{ The following model games are dedicated to the line } 1. e4 c6 2. Nf3 d5 3. d3 Qc7 4. exd5 cxd5 5. c4 Nf6 6. Nc3 { This is another principled way of using the move 3...Qc7. Besides putting pressure on d5, White is also planning to harrass the black queen by means of g2-g3 followed by Bf4. In the analysis to the model games, I prove that 6...e6 promises Black very good chances. } *[Event "USA-ch"]
