{The following model games are taken from GM Marin's database French Defence - Classical Repertoire against 3.Nd2. The idea of this bonus material is to help the reader better understand the IQP with a white pawn on c3.}  *

[Site "Moscow (m/18) 18/220"]
[Date "1974.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Karpov, Anatoly"]
[Black "Kortschnoj, Viktor"]
[Result "1/2-1/2"]
[Annotator "GM Mihail Marin"]
[ECO "C09"]
[EventDate "1974.??.??"]
