{ The following couple of model games are dedicated the the IQP type of position arising after the moves } 1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 cxd5 4. c4 Nf6 5. Nc3 g6 6. Nf3 Bg7 7. cxd5 O-O 8. Bc4 Nbd7 9. O-O Nb6 10. Qb3 Nxc4 11. Qxc4 b6 { As you will see in the analysis, White is the one who should fight for equality in this position. } *[Event "Titled Tuesday intern op 20th Dec Late"]
