{ The following 2 model games feature another favourable version of IQP for Black. We can get it after the moves } 1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 cxd5 4. c4 Nf6 5. Nc3 g6 6. Nf3 Bg7 7. h3 O-O 8. Be2 Nc6 9. O-O dxc4 10. Bxc4 Na5 { This important move is designed to chase the light-squared bishop away from the diagonal a2-g8. After the bishop's retreat, Black will play ...Be6, thus getting a very nice version of Tarrasch Defence with colours reversed. } *[Event "Maastricht Limburg op-A 11th"]
